<table>
<tr><td><strong>Total Tables:</strong></td><td>9</td><td><strong>Database Engine:</strong></td><td>SQLite</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Primary Purpose:</strong></td><td>Employee Performance Management</td><td><strong>Total Indexes:</strong></td><td>13</td></tr>
